162
00:10:05,468 --> 00:10:06,385
Apa?

163
00:10:07,386 --> 00:10:10,264
Ulang tahun Seo-jun 23 April?

164
00:10:12,350 --> 00:10:13,309
<i>Apa kau</i>

165
00:10:13,893 --> 00:10:16,979
baca <i>23 April</i> karya Kang Byeong-jun?

166
00:10:17,688 --> 00:10:20,149
