00:10:34,747 --> 00:10:36,499
BAHAN-BAHAN SPAGETI

170
00:10:36,582 --> 00:10:39,085
TOMAT, JAMUR, BAWANG,
SAUS TOMAT, SPAGETI, BAKON

171
00:10:39,168 --> 00:10:40,002
Bagus.

172
00:10:43,923 --> 00:10:45,007
Sebentar.

173
00:10:45,091 --> 00:10:48,010
Untuk makan malam besok
aku akan membuat <i>tteokbokki</i>.

174
00:10:49,971 --> 00:10:52,181
BAHAN-BAHAN <i>TTEOKBOKKI</i>

175
00:10:52,264 --> 00:10:54,225
KUE BERAS, SAUS CABAI, KECAP
DAUN BAWANG

176
00:10:54,308 --> 00:10:56,060
Saus cabai ada di rumah.

177
00:10:56,644 --> 00:10:58,187
Untuk hadiah peserta,

178
00:10:58,270 --> 00:10:59,814
kurasa buku catatan terlalu mahal.

179
00:11:00,272 --> 00:11:01,565
Kuganti pembatas buku.

180
00:11:02,984 --> 00:11:03,859
Itu ide bagus.

181
00:11:04,902 --> 00:11:07,738
Bagaimana menurutmu?
Ini terbuat dari bunga.

182
00:11:08,531 --> 00:11:10,741
- Astaga, ini bagus.
- Manis, 'kan?

183
00:11:11,450 --> 00:11:12,618
Aku mau satu.

184
00:11:13,035 --> 00:11:14,036
EUN-HO

185
00:11:17,331 --> 00:11:19,291
<i>Aku membuat spageti. Cepatlah pulang.</i>

186
00:11:29,927 --> 00:11:30,928
DAN-I

187
00:11:36,308 --> 00:11:37,977
<i>Ini hari Jumat, kakakmu berkencan.</i>

188
00:11:39,729 --> 00:11:41,439
Aku muak dengar kata "kakak".

189
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:45,151
Dia menemui Ji Seo-jun lagi?

190
00:11:45,735 --> 00:11:48,696
Dan soal kafe tempat acara membaca itu...

191
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:52,408
Bagaimana jika kita hias dindingnya
dengan lampu mini?

192
00:11:53,242 --> 00:11:54,076
Aku suka itu.

193
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:56,537
Hei, mau pesan camilan?

194
00:11:57,121 --> 00:11:58,414
Aku setuju.

195
00:11:58,497 --> 00:12:00,124
- Ide bagus.
- Mari pesan sesuatu.

196
00:12:00,207 --> 00:12:02,001
- Tunggu.
- Ambil menunya. Di sana, ya?

197
00:12:04,045 --> 00:12:05,629
- Pilihlah.
- Kita pesan apa?

198
00:12:06,839 --> 00:12:07,965
Kita harus pesan apa?

199
00:12:09,008 --> 00:12:10,885
- Tampaknya <i>jokbal</i> enak.
- Mari pesan itu.

200
00:12:10,968 --> 00:12:11,802
Baik.

201
00:12:11,886 --> 00:12:14,263
Bu Go, kami mau pesan camilan.
Kau mau juga?

202
00:12:14,346 --> 00:12:16,640
Tidak, terima kasih.
Aku akan berkemas dan pulang.

203
00:12:17,641 --> 00:12:18,476
Baiklah.

204
00:12:20,061 --> 00:12:21,395
Kenapa kau tanya dia?

205
00:12:21,896 --> 00:12:23,606
Dia mau pulang.

206
00:12:38,079 --> 00:12:39,163
Bagus untuknya.

207
00:12:39,914 --> 00:12:41,665
Dia punya dua putri.

208
00:12:51,717 --> 00:12:53,969
- Siapa yang pesan <i>jokbal</i>?
- Di sini.

209
00:12:55,471 --> 00:12:57,640
- Aku traktir.
- Tak apa-apa, aku saja.

210
00:12:57,765 --> 00:12:59,767
Taruh di sini.

211
00:13:01,102 --> 00:13:03,187
- Satu <i>jokbal</i> porsi besar?
- Ya.

212
00:13:07,024 --> 00:13:08,818
Kujamin ini akan enak.

213
00:13:08,901 --> 00:13:11,070
Istriku memasaknya dari awal.

214
00:13:11,195 --> 00:13:13,781
Kebanyakan restoran
menjual yang cepat saji.

215
00:13:13,864 --> 00:13:14,824
Tidak pernah enak.

216
00:13:23,207 --> 00:13:25,251
- Kau pernah menikah?
- Tidak.

217
00:13:27,378 --> 00:13:28,754
Aku hanya sempat berfoto.

218
00:13:29,547 --> 00:13:31,757
Tanggal hari H sudah ada,
tapi seseorang kabur.

219
00:13:31,841 --> 00:13:34,885
- Si berengsek itu?
- Tidak, aku.

220
